dc_title_s: Infrastructure Report Geodatabase - Pipelines permitted as of December 2012: Pennsylvania
dc_description_s: This dataset represents pipelines where construction has been started or completed before December 31, 2012 and permitted through a DCNR natural gas lease or developed on state forest lands where DCNR does not own the mineral rights.Pipeline Type Code Values: 1=Gathering, 2=Marketing, 3=Water, 4=Other or Unknown, 5=Meter/Valve/Tap, 6=Trunk
dc_publisher_sm: Pennsylvania Department of Conservation and Natural Resources
